To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private HaramiCross _haramicross;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_haramicross = HaramiCross(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_haramicross.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "haramicross", _haramicross.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.haramicross = self.HaramiCross(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.haramicross.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "haramicross", self.haramicross.Current.Value)
